{"tid":624862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"街場打籃底係咪可以用手推開人囉位?","createTime":"2018-04-11T03:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T04:35:48.000Z","uid":57786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"747d1bfeee0c639a9edb26cf2a655b51acc5373e","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"法國啲阿叔好鍾意咁做<br />\n8 90年代nba係咪咁打???<br />\n<br />\n頂多佢幾次，完全放棄了<br />\n由得佢推走我算了"},{"pid":"ea2949b871e0d7a7ef37c75274e38c645f2591a6","tid":624862,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意用條J頂人屎忽"},{"pid":"e261789ffc62d2b37b703ee5328d4fc751ffe5da","tid":624862,"uid":78425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"多數矮仔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2ea9368e9549806092c5ff585d50e587abba74","tid":624862,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"藍波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a564caca28cda157f97576a547116047c684b32c","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://shuwst.pixnet.net/blog/post/273756815-籃球場上常見的30種犯規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshuwst.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F273756815-%E7%B1%83%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%8430%E7%A8%AE%E7%8A%AF%E8%A6%8F&d=rl0hN6gtZXEZsXlO8Z7T2zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=54d3f457\" target=\"_blank\">https://shuwst.pixnet.net/blog/post/273756815-籃球場上常見的30種犯規</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爭搶籃板球時，被卡在後面的球員試圖跳起去搶球，而越過已卡好位子球員的圓柱體原則，如此去「侵犯到對方身體」也算推人。<br />\n<br />\n假設我被卡在矮仔後面，跳起伸手去佢頭頂拎籃板但冇掂到佢都犯規???"},{"pid":"facb84ad243a5f3f3e39767a848e3740e56d92f2","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea2949b871e0d7a7ef37c75274e38c645f2591a6","tid":624862,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意用條J頂人屎忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"在禁區籃底下，進攻球員用屁股或肩膀去頂開已佔好位置的防守者，甚至，用非持球手「拐開防守者」，以上皆稱進攻犯規。<br />\n<br />\n用J頂開對手好似唔犯規<br />\n<br />\n假設進攻者攝去卡好位嘅防守者前面，再用背部全身迫開防守者，咁有冇犯規?"},{"pid":"85fb92e769ff84f9db6dc6763b4a1076be0b5056","tid":624862,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a564caca28cda157f97576a547116047c684b32c","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://shuwst.pixnet.net/blog/post/273756815-籃球場上常見的30種犯規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshuwst.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F273756815-%E7%B1%83%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%8430%E7%A8%AE%E7%8A%AF%E8%A6%8F&d=rl0hN6gtZXEZsXlO8Z7T2zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=54d3f457\" target=\"_blank\">https://shuwst.pixnet.net/blog/post/273756815-籃球場上常見的30種犯規</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爭搶籃板球時，被卡在後面的球員試圖跳起去搶球，而越過已卡好位子球員的圓柱體原則，如此去「侵犯到對方身體」也算推人。<br />\n<br />\n假設我被卡在矮仔後面，跳起伸手去佢頭頂拎籃板但冇掂到佢都犯規???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"冇掂到佢梗係唔算犯規，但你從上方下壓（即係壓到佢膊頭/壓到佢頭），或者從佢身後有個力令佢移咗位，都係你犯規。<br />\n<br />\n只不過你都講係街場喇，街場規則/尺度日日都唔同，籃球鼓勵<span style=\"color: red;\">一定程度</span>嘅肉搏，即係喺籃底係可以你推我頂咁（呢個時候，話唔定你嘅例子就唔會吹foul），下下掂到都話FOUL咁嘅高敏感尺度，比賽咪變成個個5犯畢業囉。"},{"pid":"c21f4154548d57eeb5c8462816d5dabafceba558","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fb92e769ff84f9db6dc6763b4a1076be0b5056","tid":624862,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a564caca28cda157f97576a547116047c684b32c","tid":624862,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://shuwst.pixnet.net/blog/post/273756815-籃球場上常見的30種犯規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https